; Issue: https://github.com/rustledger/rustledger/issues/365
; Description: Glob patterns in include directives not supported
; Expected: Glob patterns like *.beancount should be expanded
;
; This test verifies that include directives with glob patterns work correctly.

option "operating_currency" "USD"

2024-01-01 open Assets:Bank USD
2024-01-01 open Expenses:Food USD
2024-01-01 open Equity:Opening-Balances USD

2024-01-01 * "Opening balance"
  Assets:Bank  1000 USD
  Equity:Opening-Balances

include "issue-365-includes/*.beancount"

; After opening balance (1000) minus groceries (50) minus dinner (30) = 920
2024-12-31 balance Assets:Bank 920 USD
